Package common.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Actable
    The common interface for actable game objects in the game.
    AnimalObserver
    Applies observer design pattern.
    Changeable
    This interface provides methods to change the image of an object.
    Displayable
    This interface provides methods to display models in the view.
    Movable  
    ObservableAnimal  
    Sinkable
    This interface provides method(s) for physical objects to sink into water and emerge from water.
